Computes an MD5 checksum from columns

Source: R/digest_to_checksum.R
digest_to_checksum.Rd

Computes an MD5 checksum from columns

Usage

digest_to_checksum(.data, col = "checksum", exclude = NULL, warn = TRUE)

Arguments

.data

A data frame, a tibble, a data.table or a tbl.

col

Name of the column to put the checksums in

exclude

Columns to exclude from the checksum generation

warn

Flag to warn if target column already exists in data

Value

.data with an checksum column added

Examples

digest_to_checksum(mtcars)
